In this project we are going to build a live chat application...
We have imported following libraries as of now...
    1. Spring Web
    2. Lombok
    3. Thymeleaf
    4. WebSocket

What is WebSocket?
It helps in maintaining continuous 2 way communication. Real time connection

What is STOMP \\Simple Text Oriented Messaging Protocol?
It gives structure to the way communication takes place. Organising the messages. Like Http, its a protocol for messages

What is message broking?
The way of routing messages. It is a middle man, it will direct the message in right place

What is SockJs?
SockJS is a JavaScript library that provides a WebSocket-like object for low-latency, cross-browser communication
We use this because, WebSocket is not supported by all the browsers. SockJs creates a stimulation of WebSocket, there by resolving the issue.
<script src="https://cdn.jsdelivr.net/npm/sockjs-client@1/dist/sockjs.min.js"></script> to add this